      • makeStudyName

        public static java.lang.String makeStudyName(java.lang.String name)
        Filter a name to create one which is acceptable for use as a Study name. The filter removes all characters except underscore, period, a-z, A-Z, and 0-9. If the result is an empty string, it assigns the name "__bullpen".
        Parameters:
        name - a proposed name for a Study.
        Returns:
        the filtered name.
